# Home Widget Action Buttons

Home summary card action buttons (`WidgetActionButton` and similar inline CTAs) must always use a **white** style.

## Style

- Background: `bg-white`
- Text: `text-gray-900`
- Border: `border-gray-200`
- Interaction: `cursor-pointer`, `hover:bg-gray-50`, `hover:border-gray-300`, `disabled:cursor-not-allowed`
- No colored backgrounds (`bg-amber-50`, `bg-emerald-50`, `bg-rose-50`, etc.)
- No colored text/borders for semantic states

## Selected state

Use a subtle neutral emphasis instead of color:

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD
className="bg-white text-gray-900 border-gray-200 ring-1 ring-gray-900"

// ❌ BAD
className="bg-amber-50 text-amber-700 border-amber-100"
className="bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 border-emerald-100"
```

## Scope

This applies to action buttons inside home widgets (Bugün kartları, meal planner, suggest, activities, series, gym, etc.). Icon badges and card headers may keep their accent colors; only the small action/CTA buttons stay white.
